trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter to convert <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"></xref> objects to and from various other types.
trans-unit.target: Gir et typen konverteringsprogram til å konvertere <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref> objekter til og fra ulike datatyper.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> class represents a single date or a range of dates.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>klassen representerer en enkelt dato eller et datoområde.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>

trans-unit.source: This class is commonly associated with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> control, where it represents the selected and highlighted dates.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er vanligvis knyttet til den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>kontrollere, der den representerer valgte og merkede datoene.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRangeConverter class is an adjunct class to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> that enables you to convert to and from other types, most often strings.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SelectionRangeConverter er en adjunct klasse til <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>som gjør det mulig å konvertere til og fra andre typer, strenger oftest.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>

trans-unit.source: For more information about type converters, see the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> base class, [Generalized Type Conversion](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), and [How to: Implement a Type Converter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om typen konverteringsprogrammer i <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>basisklasse, [Generalized typekonvertering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), og [slik: implementere et konverteringsprogram av typen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter> class is specialized to convert between the types <xref:System.String> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter>Klassen er spesielle for å konvertere mellom typer <xref:System.String>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> </xref:System.String> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter>
